<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #FAEBD7;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #F5F5DC;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #2E8B57;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .text-center {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .display-4 {
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #8B0000;
        }

        .lead {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #556B2F;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #8B0000;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

            .btn:hover {
                background-color: #6B8E23;
            }

        .row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .col-md-4 {
            flex: 0 0 30%;
            background-color: #FFF8DC;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

            .col-md-4 h2 {
                color: #2E8B57;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }

            .col-md-4 p {
                font-size: 1em;
                color: #333;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

        <div class="text-center">
            <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to Canada's Finest Apples</h1>
            <p class="lead">Home to the Best Apples in the World</p>
            <hr />
            <p>Discover our wide variety of premium apples, grown with love and care in the lush orchards of Canada.</p>
            <p><a href="/apples" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Explore Our Apples</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <p>We have been cultivating the finest apples for over a century. Our dedication to quality and sustainability ensures that every apple is perfect.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h2>Varieties</h2>
                <p>From crisp and tart to sweet and juicy, we offer a variety of apple types to suit every palate. Our apples are picked at peak ripeness for maximum flavor.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h2>Where to Buy</h2>
                <p>Find out where you can purchase our delicious apples, whether at a local farmer's market, grocery store, or online.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>